    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every service milestone. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is the one. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
