    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade FD3S RX-7, maintained to an exacting standard. This example retains its numbers-matching 13B-REW rotary powerplant, featuring a healthy sequential twin-turbocharger setup with flawless transition and no vacuum leaks. The chassis remains structurally pristine, boasting original double-wishbone suspension geometry and a Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Recent compression testing confirms robust, even pulses across all rotor faces. Finished in its factory-original paint with documented service history, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning enthusiast seeking mechanical purity and peak performance.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
