    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality masterpiece that satisfies even the most meticulous collector. This vehicle has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one, and it shows. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes, and has been treated with a multi-layer ceramic coating for lasting protection. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium upholstery remains taut with no bolster wear, and the factory-fresh aroma persists. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the smallest ambient light, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It rides on its original wheels, which are entirely free of curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with ample tread. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example of automotive excellence that looks and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48950.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
